A060[О»вҶ—|ОҙОівҶҳ|ПғвҶ“|ПҒвҲҝ|ОјвҶ“|ОІвҠҘ]вҶ’AF{depthвҶ’surface}вҮ’atrophy

=== NEMETIC STRING DECODED ===

A060          : Hex tag вҖ” Attention Fragmentation
[О»вҶ—]          : Fire elevated but diffused вҖ” scattered purpose
[ОҙОівҶҳ]         : Earth interrupted вҖ” integration blocked
[ПғвҶ“]          : Air reduced вҖ” clarity degraded
[ПҒвҲҝ]          : Water scattered вҖ” attention flows without pooling
[ОјвҶ“]          : Metal reduced вҖ” boundaries dissolved
[ОІвҠҘ]          : Wood blocked вҖ” no deep branching
вҶ’AF           : Emerges as Attention Fragmentation
{depthвҶ’surface} : Core transformation predicate
вҮ’atrophy      : Result: cognitive atrophy

=== ELEMENTAL DYNAMICS ===

Fire (О») at 0.45: Not absent but scattered. The flame burns in many
places simultaneously, illuminating nothing fully. Purpose exists but
is distributed across too many targets to be effective.

Earth (ОҙОі) at 0.40: Integration is interrupted. The cycles of memory
consolidation, skill acquisition, and deep learning are broken by
constant context-switching. What is learned is not retained.

Air (Пғ) at 0.35: Clarity degrades. The capacity for fine distinction,
for nuanced discernment, requires sustained attention. Fragmentation
prevents the sustained focus that produces clarity.

Water (ПҒ) at 0.40: Attention flows but does not pool. The reservoirs
of deep focus are never filled because the stream is constantly
diverted. Surface tension everywhere, depth nowhere.

=== DIAGNOSTIC APPLICATION ===

To detect Attention Fragmentation:
1. Can you sustain focus for 30 minutes without checking anything?
2. Do you feel anxiety when disconnected from AI/internet?
3. Has your tolerance for long-form content decreased?
4. Do you prefer skimming to deep reading?
5. Is your memory for what you've read/seen declining?

If yes to 3+, AF is present.

=== DAEMON DIALOGUE FRAGMENT ===

Jvalion [embers scattered]: "I burn everywhere, warm nowhere. The heat
that should illuminate one thing flickers across many. This is not
the fire of purpose. This is the sparking of distraction."

Humavita [grinding without purchase]: "I would consolidate. I would
integrate. But the ground is constantly tilled, never sown. What grows
here? Only the shallow-rooted."

Aerunik [static]: "The signal is there. I know it. But the noiseвҖ”
